chore: scaffold monorepo, web/api/mcp packages, base configs

Initialize pnpm workspace with turbo monorepo for MCP-powered hyperlocal events app.

Apps:
- apps/web: Next.js 15 + App Router + Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui (port 3000)
- apps/api: Express + Prisma + Redis + BullMQ (port 4000)

Packages:
- packages/mcp-server: @modelcontextprotocol/sdk with custom tools
- packages/ui: shadcn/ui Button and Card components
- packages/core: Shared Zod schemas, types, and utilities
- packages/config: ESLint, TypeScript, and Tailwind configs

Infrastructure:
- Docker Compose: PostgreSQL 15 + PostGIS, Redis 7
- Prisma schema with geospatial support
- Multi-stage Dockerfiles for production builds

Features:
- Health check endpoint: GET /health -> {ok:true}
- Minimal landing page with Lucide icons
- Structured logging with Pino
- Security middleware (Helmet, CORS)
- Workspace scripts: dev, build, lint, type-check, test, format

Quality gates: ✅ lint, ✅ type-check, ✅ build, ✅ format
